	<td class="bugnote-note-public">
		After having discussed this issue with osarrat, we have agreed upon the following:<br />
- rather than a button, the navigation panel to the left will enable returning to the lists of models<br />
- graphical enhancement: current tab will be marked as active by a lighter background in the panel	</td>
